author: Jonathan Sawyer
title: Lil Yachty & The Sailing Team Unveil the Urban Outfitters x Nautica Spring 2017 Collection
text:
Visit the original post to see all 13 images from this gallery. 
Brand: Nautica
Season: Spring 2017
Key Pieces: Multicolored windbreaker, blue pullover hoodie, yellow long-sleeve T-shirt, navy swim trunks.
Editor’s Notes: For the second installment in their collaborative partnership, Urban Outfitters and Nautica have tapped Lil Yachty and his Sailing Team to star in the new Spring 2017 campaign. The nine-piece collection in turn consists of men’s apparel and accessories, including a windbreaker, long-sleeve tee, long-sleeve polo, short-sleeve graphic tee, pullover hoodie sweatshirt, two swim shorts, and two baseball hats, each featuring bold primary colors of yellows, oranges and blues, with graphic colorblocking and mesh details throughout, reminiscent of vintage ’90s Nautica sportswear.
The UO x Nautica Spring 2017 arsenal arrives Monday, March 27th in select Urban Outfitters stores and via urbanoutfitters.com .
